data.description: Are you wanting a great home with plenty of space for you and your favorite pets? This amazing property is on a paved road less than 5 miles from HWY 89. It features 2.81 acres, fully fenced,  Two 50 AMP Full RV Hook-ups. 50 GPM Private Well and 1250 Septic!!  2019 Cavco 1152 sq ft single wide with a front porch TREX deck. It is a spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath with an open concept in the kitchen/dining/ living room. Insulated Detached garage with side carport. Amazing insulated She Shed. There is also a custom built Well house.  Irrigated landscape with grass and fruit trees. Beautiful country space yet close enough to shopping and schools. Bring your animals and enjoy this beautiful space!
